# PetReminder — Proje Gereksinimler Analizi

Hocanın sitesindeki gereksinimler vs. mevcut proje durumu karşılaştırması.

> [!TIP]
> ✅ = Tamam | ⚠️ = Kısmi | ❌ = Eksik

---

## 1. Kod & Mimari (Benim Düzeltebileceğim)

| Gereksinim | Durum | Detay |
|---|---|---|
| Modüler mimari (lib / app ayrımı) | ⚠️ | Tek modül (`petreminder-app`), `lib` ayrı değil |
| IRepository\<T\> interface | ✅ | [save](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#133-155), [findById](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#156-173), [findAll](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#174-191), [update](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#192-206), [delete](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#207-221) + [deleteAll](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#222-233), [count](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#234-248), [close](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/SqliteRepository.java#249-263) |
| BinaryRepository\<T\> | ✅ | Dosya tabanlı, Serializable |
| SqliteRepository\<T\> | ✅ | JDBC ile çalışıyor |
| MySqlRepository\<T\> | ✅ | MySQL Connector/J |
| RepositoryFactory | ✅ | `createPetRepository()`, `createReminderRepository()` vb. |
| Runtime storage switch | ✅ | [StorageConfig](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/config/StorageConfig.java#23-176) + ConsoleApp/SettingsPanel |
| docker-compose.yml (MySQL) | ✅ | Root dizinde mevcut |
| 100% Unit test coverage | ⚠️ | 488 test geçiyor, ama **JaCoCo %100 değil** (coverage raporu kontrol edilmeli) |
| Doxygen dokümantasyon | ⚠️ | [Doxyfile](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/Doxyfile) mevcut, ama `docs/` çıktı dizini yok |
| Swing GUI | ✅ | `MainFrame`, paneller, diyaloglar mevcut |
| MVC Pattern | ⚠️ | Model ve Service var, ama Controller ayrı bir katman değil |
| Console UI | ✅ | [ConsoleApp.java](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/ConsoleApp.java) mevcut |
| Encapsulation | ✅ | Tüm alanlar private, getter/setter mevcut |
| Inheritance | ✅ | [Pet](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/service/PetService.java#52-64) → [Dog](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/model/Dog.java#17-100), [Cat](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/test/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/PetSqliteRepositoryTest.java#65-74), [Bird](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/test/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/PetSqliteRepositoryTest.java#75-84) / [Reminder](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/test/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/service/ReminderServiceTest.java#43-51) → alt sınıflar |
| Polymorphism | ✅ | [makeSound()](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/model/Dog.java#76-82), `getReminderType()`, [validate()](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/service/PetService.java#159-173) override'ları |
| Interfaces (min. 2) | ✅ | [IRepository](file:///c:/Users/mehdi/Documents/github/%C3%BCniversite/cen-206-38-mehdi-karagulle-java/petreminder-app/src/main/java/com/mehdi/petreminder/repository/IRepository.java#23-81), `Serializable` |
| Design Patterns (min. 3) | ⚠️ | Factory (✅ RepositoryFactory), Template Method (✅ SqliteRepository), Observer (❌ yok) |
| SOLID Principles | ⚠️ | SRP ve DIP uygulanmış, ama dokümante edilmemiş |
| CHANGELOG | ❌ | `CHANGELOG.md` dosyası yok |

